settings.title: Certificates of Analysis (COA)
settings.warning_statements:
Contains: THC

  • This product is intended for use only by adults 21 years and older. Keep out of reach of children.
  • There may be health risks associated with the consumption of this product.
  • There may be additional health risks associated with the consumption of this product for women who are pregnant, breastfeeding, or plan to become pregnant.
  • This statement has not been evaluated by the Food and Drug Administration. This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease.
  • The intoxicating effects of this product maybe delayed by two or more hours.
  • Do not drive a motor vehicle or operate machinery while using this product.
  • Use of this product may result in a positive drug screen.
